IMAPAccount gmail
Host imap.gmail.com
User gustavo.calvo.cr@gmail.com
PassCmd "pass personal/gmail.com/gustavo.calvo.cr@gmail.com"
TLSType IMAPS
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

IMAPStore gmail-remote
Account gmail

MaildirStore gmail-local
SubFolders Verbatim
Path ~/.local/share/isync/gmail/
Inbox ~/.local/share/isync/gmail/Inbox

Channel gmail
Far :gmail-remote:
Near :gmail-local:
Patterns * ![Gmail]* "[Gmail]/Sent Mail" "[Gmail]/Starred" "[Gmail]/All Mail" "[Gmail]/Trash"
Create Both
# Sync the movement of messages between folders and deletions, add after making sure the sync works
#Expunge Both
SyncState *
